      <akn:section eId="sec_47_4665_03">
        <akn:num>47-4665.03</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>The Advisory Board Company — compliance.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-4665_03_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If the Mayor, pursuant to § 2-219.03a, determines that the Company is in compliance with the hiring requirements of §§ 47-4665.01 through 47-4665.05 and the incentive agreement, the Company shall be deemed to be in compliance with the provisions of part A of subchapter X of Chapter 2 of Title 2 of the District of Columbia Official Code.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-4665_03_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>On or before October 31, the Company shall provide the Mayor with the following information pertaining to the previous tax year:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-4665_03_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Company shall comply with the requirements contained in § 2-218.46, with regard to the Project.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
